HEADWORD: Potoroo
<hw>Po`to*roo"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any small kangaroo belonging to <gen>Hypsiprymnus</gen>,
<gen>Bettongia</gen>, and allied genera, native of Australia and
Tasmania. Called also <altname>kangaroo rat</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Potpie</ent>⟦br⟧
